# Backend clean architecture

## Layers (`backend/src/`)

| Layer | Path | Contains |
|-------|------|----------|
| Application | `application/use-cases/` | `*UseCase.execute()` — business logic |
| Infrastructure | `infrastructure/` | Prisma, Yapily, encryption, BullMQ |
| Interfaces | `interfaces/http/`, `interfaces/webhooks/` | Controllers, guards — thin |

## New endpoint checklist

1. Zod schema → `packages/validators/`
2. DTO → `packages/shared-types/` (if new shape)
3. Use case → `application/use-cases/<feature>/`
4. Controller + module → `interfaces/http/<feature>/`
5. Register in `http-api.module.ts`
6. Gateways needed? `imports: [YapilyModule]` in feature module

## Inject gateways correctly

```typescript
// ✅
constructor(@Inject(PIS_GATEWAY) private readonly pis: PisGateway) {}

// ❌ — direct Yapily HTTP in use case
```

## Controllers stay thin

```typescript
// ✅
@Post('login')
login(@Body() body: unknown) {
  return this.loginUser.execute(body);
}
```

## Prisma

- Schema: `backend/prisma/schema.prisma`
- Dev migrate: `pnpm prisma migrate dev`
- Prod migrate: `prisma migrate deploy` (Docker entrypoint)

## Tests

`backend/test/*.test.ts` — Node test runner + tsx. Add tests for gateways/factories, not trivial wiring.
